headline: NetApp Builds AI Infrastructure On NVIDIA AI Data Platform
summary: NetApp, Inc. (NASDAQ:NTAP) has moved to capitalize on the growing need for intelligent data infrastructure amid the ever-increasing adoption of AI to solve complex business challenges. On May 19, it inked a strategic partnership with Nvidia to accelerate NVIDIA AI Data Platform integration in the NetApp AIPod solution. The ultimate goal is to accelerate agentic […]
